Transcription.Text: In the preliminary experiments, the tracer was added to a liter of effluent and immediately coprecipitated with strontium sulphate from hot solution. Complete exchange was obtained by acidifying the effluent with five milliliters of concentrated nitric acid and boiling for more than half an hour before completing the coprecipitation.
